paragraphs.title: utmContent visits
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as(
    select * from(
    select guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(appLaunch)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))>='2023-02-01'
    union 
    select firstGuid as guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(sessionSummary)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000))>='2023-02-01'
    ) order by guid
)

select utmContent, count(distinct sessionId) as visits from cte where lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' group by utmContent
",1000)

paragraphs.title: FTU_RTU_Visits
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as(
    select * from(
    select guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(appLaunch)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))>='2023-02-01'
    union 
    select firstGuid as guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(sessionSummary)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000))>='2023-02-01'
    ) order by guid
)

select case when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_APP_D1V_visits'
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_APP_D1V_visits'
        else 'others'
end as Channel, count (distinct sessionId) as visits
from cte
group by Channel
",1000)
